    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable, no-frills daily driver or a budget-friendly project. While the engine and transmission are in working order and the car is fully drivable, there are visible signs of age including several noticeable scratches on the body and some fading in the paintwork. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there are minor electrical quirks, such as a slow power window and an aging infotainment screen. It has been maintained enough to stay on the road, but it will likely need routine suspension work and a deep clean to bring it back to its best. This is an honest car at an honest price for a buyer who prioritizes function over aesthetics.",
