      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2008 Chevrolet Corvette Z06 is a purist\u2019s performance machine, powered by the hand-assembled 7.0L LS7 V8 with a dry-sump oiling system. The powertrain is mated to a Tremec TR-6060 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a hydroformed aluminum chassis, magnesium roof structure, and carbon-fiber composite floor panels for optimal power-to-weight ratio. The valvetrain has been professionally addressed with hardened valve guides and Ti-intake valves to ensure long-term reliability. Suspension geometry remains tight with factory monotube dampers and transverse leaf springs. Braking is handled by 6-piston front and 4-piston rear calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing exceptional thermal management. A mechanically sound example ready for spirited apex-hunting.",
